    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T22:07:57.699+09:00">inversely born (legs first)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-16a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T22:29:01.689+09:00">is a （cliffy city：）city among cliffs.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-16a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T22:36:37.026+09:00">it's best soon to make for him a(place:)residence,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-17a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T22:44:57.864+09:00">Since he is not righteous,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-17a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T22:46:25.419+09:00">[the people] will not be (attached to:)devoted.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T22:53:19.107+09:00">T-wan built ready[his defences] and collected [his grain].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-21a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T23:01:44.695+09:00">Oh,I alone have none</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-21a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-10T23:06:50.031+09:00">Its joy is very genial(harmonious).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-70a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T17:34:22.536+09:00">those who, when indignant, can be calmly dignified,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-70a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T17:34:36.306+09:00">are few.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-70a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:08:10.887+09:00">the small bully the great</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-82a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:12:56.366+09:00">With our troops,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-83a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:16:15.502+09:00">he relies on his troops and finds his safety in (cruelty:)severity,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-83a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:20:14.381+09:00">The weapon,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-83a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:20:27.67+09:00">are like fire;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-83a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:21:42.591+09:00">if you do not call them in (followed Yen Shi-ku),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-83a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:21:57.787+09:00">you will burn yourself.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-98a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:28:35.755+09:00">I will make a round-tour(inspection tour)of the land.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-114a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:36:30.438+09:00">Men from Cheng came</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-115a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:36:14.548+09:00">and (conveyed:)made offer of peace.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-119a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:37:41.19+09:00">If one prolongs evil without changing,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-119a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-11T18:39:46.927+09:00">as a consequence, it will (reach:) befall oneself.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_008-357a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-12T17:39:32.343+09:00">Sun Po did not bring back his followers(he fled alone)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-173a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-12T17:44:04.316+09:00">If the foremost(i.e. Cheng's weak vanguard)are captured,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-173a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-12T17:44:16.773+09:00">they(the Jung)will be eager to advance.  (follow Kung Ying-da)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:07:17.858+09:00">You have condescended to tsai be with me(to stop at my place).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:08:10.931+09:00">When Chou presides over covenants,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:09:45.101+09:00">[priences of]different clans (than the Ki)are placed last.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:10:10.014+09:00">On the mountains there are trees,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:11:05.439+09:00">but it is the carpenter who measures them,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:12:21.588+09:00">for guests(princes of different clans)there are ritual rules,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-198a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:15:03.375+09:00">but it is the (one who c h u presides)the president(over the covenant)who selects them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-203a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:19:54.283+09:00">You say that Hu does not furnish [its tributes],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-204a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:23:28.57+09:00">Even my few kinsmen I have not been able to s i a n g y i be at peace with.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-204a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:28:31.353+09:00">I also rely on it(your help) in order to strengthen my boders.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-205a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:28:59.906+09:00">It is rites</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-205a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:31:41.561+09:00">that regulate the state</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-205a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:32:34.736+09:00"> and (classify:)establish the classes among the people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_001-205a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:33:13.911+09:00">(sc.distinguish high and low).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-28a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:44:54.184+09:00">He shall make brilliant the virtue and  promoted the perverse (wicked)[man].  (follows Kung Ying-ta)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-28a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:46:15.918+09:00">the cereals are not refined.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-28a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:48:27.687+09:00">The 5 colours and the emblems</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-28a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:49:32.835+09:00"> illustrate his [choice of] quality.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-28a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T11:52:03.897+09:00">for the increase and decrease (sc. in the long row of emblems just describes) there are proper numbers.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-40a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T12:12:59.375+09:00">the inferiors will not peep at[ the superiors]and have desires(ambitions).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-85a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-13T12:22:06.685+09:00">an opposing[force] to the left.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-85a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-14T21:37:54.894+09:00">he made a y u-l i(fish-faster:)fish-trap battle array;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-86a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-14T21:39:48.75+09:00">The files of 5 foot-soldiers were responsible for the closing up(of the forces)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-102a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-14T21:46:40.596+09:00">It expresses that they(the animals)do not suffer from swollenness(boils).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-101a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-14T22:10:56.685+09:00">We have displayed(follows Yu Yue,as p e i is parallel to c h a n g)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-101a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:15:47.083+09:00">  our buff-coats and weapons.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-105a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:22:16.555+09:00">People from T'si presented them victual with forage and firewood.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-108a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:25:37.984+09:00">He(the prince)received[him](the new-born son)with a t'ai l ao [feast].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-109a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:29:12.494+09:00">To give [a baby]name according to s h e n g a birth[phenomenom](e.g. a significant birthmark) is called sin (a true-making)a realization.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-109a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:31:50.819+09:00">The Chou with taboo names served the [ancestral]Spirits,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-109a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:31:51.542+09:00">m i n g the personal name,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-109a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:32:34.701+09:00">c h u n g after death one should taboo it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-142a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:36:52.74+09:00">Thus they battled,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-142a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:37:39.237+09:00">but fled.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-142a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:39:10.163+09:00">They turned their backs to the army of P -a.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-168a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:43:48.983+09:00">The Yun have anxious hearts and rely [only] on their walls</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-168a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:44:31.271+09:00">They think anxiously about the arrival.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-197a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:48:22.078+09:00">The mo-ao general has become(slighting:) disdainful through the action at Pu-sao.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_009-127a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:52:49.294+09:00">[one single man—you must not treat him(familiar:) disdainfully,how much the less a state?]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-197a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T00:56:54.294+09:00">the Heaven is not (acceding, approaching:) accommodating and easy.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-244a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T01:02:34.288+09:00">Suan Kiang and Kung-ts,Shuo entangled Ki-tsi.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-265a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T01:14:28.265+09:00">He requited the wickedness to the highest degree.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_002-279a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T23:33:21.652+09:00">Two equal queens (a concubine having equal rights as the queen), two equal first-rank sons,two governments.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_012-285a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T23:35:03.758+09:00">Chuang Kung would harm the old ministers and wished to remove them all.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-83a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-15T23:55:30.612+09:00">Kao Yao went and (sowed:)spread his virtue.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-88a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T00:29:46.586+09:00">He scoldingly demanded the shoe from his foot-solider Pi.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-88a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T00:53:25.211+09:00">Should I oppose you? (how should I prevent you from entering and killing the prince.)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-103a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T00:55:42.671+09:00">by courier car he returned.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-113a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T00:57:37.095+09:00">why then should you find fault with them?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-113a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:00:00.884+09:00">Clothes and food are what I (find my peace in,get satisfaction from:)get my comfort from.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-113a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:03:43.862+09:00">I always go by the real circumstances.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-116a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:07:44.003+09:00">m e n g putting on k a o envelopping p'i(leopards:）leopard skins,he first went to attack them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-126a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:11:24.926+09:00">If by ambuscade one defeats it,it is called...</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-128a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:13:31.198+09:00">Their (ascent) prosperity was a sudden rising.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-128a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:16:44.872+09:00">Their ruin was swift.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-130a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:18:33.405+09:00">The price of Sung (strapped, restrained:) rebuked him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_003-158a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#minmin" modified="2024-12-16T01:20:39.744+09:00">You have no words from the inside[for me].</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
